query:
INSERT INTO "DocumentSummary" (
                document_id,   
                version_id, 
                summary
            )
            SELECT 
                u.document_id, u.version_id, u.summary
            FROM 
                UNNEST($1::text[], $2::text[], $3::text[])
                AS u(document_id, version_id, summary)
            RETURNING 
                id as "id?",  
                "createdAt" as "created_at?: DateTime<Utc>",
                document_id,
                version_id, 
                summary
